# ta-URT: Lytollis Bounded Chaos — Cross-Domain Validation

One repo. One click. Seven domains.  
**Contractive core H + bounded adaptive Ψ ⇒ chaos shaped, stability guaranteed.**

[![Open in GitHub Codespaces](https://github.com/codespaces/badge.svg)](https://github.com/codespaces/new?hide_repo_select=true&ref=main)
[![CI](https://github.com/${GITHUB_REPOSITORY}/actions/workflows/ci.yml/badge.svg)](./.github/workflows/ci.yml)
